title: 18. Breaking Down Your Ingredient Labels! Important Ingredients To Know In Skincare: Part 1
description:
Hey everyone! In today's episode we are getting into some of the key players for you to know as estheticians and as someone buying and consuming skincare. The good, bad, and the necessary-- here's what we love using in the treatment room + look for on ingredient labels. Xo, Tess and Lo

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly
